<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Last Will and Testament</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #000;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #000;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2em;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    h3 {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-top: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: justify;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .signature-block {
      margin-top: 50px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .signature-item {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 250px;
      margin: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px dashed #000;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      text-align: center;
      color: #444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>WILL OF <%= testator.name %></h1>

  <p>I, <strong><%= testator.name %></strong>, son of <strong><%= testator.sonOf %></strong>, residing at <strong><%= testator.residingAt %></strong>, declare this to be my LAST WILL being made on <strong><%= testator.willDate %></strong>.</p>

  <p>I revoke all prior wills, codicils and testamentary dispositions previously made by me. I am in good health and of sound mind, and not making this will under any persuasion or coercion.</p>

  <p>I give, devise, and bequeath all remaining movable and immovable assets, financial and physical assets owned by me and belonging to no one else to the following Beneficiaries as mentioned in this Will:</p>

  <h2>List of Beneficiaries</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>S.N.</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Relationship</th>
        <th>PAN / Aadhar</th>
        <th>Residence</th>
        <th>Age</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% beneficiaries.forEach((b, index) => { %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
          <td><%= b.name %></td>
          <td><%= b.relationship %></td>
          <td><%= b.panAadhar %></td>
          <td><%= b.residence %></td>
          <td><%= b.age %></td>
        </tr>
      <% }) %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>Below is the list of assets and percentage share of each asset I would like to transfer to the above Beneficiaries:</p>

  <h2>Movable Assets - Financial</h2>
  <% if (bankAccounts.length) { %>
    <h3>Bank Accounts</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Bank</th>
          <th>Account No</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% bankAccounts.forEach((acc, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= acc.bankName %></td>
            <td><%= acc.accountNumber %></td>
            <td><%= acc.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= acc.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= acc.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <% if (insurancePolicies.length) { %>
    <h3>Insurance Policies</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Policy Name</th>
          <th>Policy No</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% insurancePolicies.forEach((ip, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= ip.nameOfPolicy %></td>
            <td><%= ip.policyNumber %></td>
            <td><%= ip.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= ip.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= ip.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <% if (stocks.length) { %>
    <h3>Stocks</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Brokerage Firm</th>
          <th>Account No</th>
          <th>Type / Remark</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% stocks.forEach((s, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= s.brokerageFirm %></td>
            <td><%= s.accountNo %></td>
            <td><%= s.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= s.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= s.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <% if (mutualFunds.length) { %>
    <h3>Mutual Funds</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Distributor</th>
          <th>Account No</th>
          <th>Type / Remark</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% mutualFunds.forEach((mf, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= mf.mfDistributor %></td>
            <td><%= mf.accountNo %></td>
            <td><%= mf.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= mf.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= mf.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <h2>Movable Assets - Physical</h2>
  <% if (jewellery.length) { %>
    <h3>Jewellery</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Invoice No</th>
          <th>Remark</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% jewellery.forEach((j, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= j.typeOfJewellery %></td>
            <td><%= j.invoiceNumber %></td>
            <td><%= j.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= j.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= j.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <h2>Immovable Assets</h2>
  <% if (house.length) { %>
    <h3>House Properties</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Name</th>
          <th>Reg. No</th>
          <th>Remark</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% house.forEach((h, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= h.nameOfProperty %></td>
            <td><%= h.registrationNumber %></td>
            <td><%= h.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= h.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= h.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <% if (land.length) { %>
    <h3>Land Properties</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>S.N.</th>
          <th>Name</th>
          <th>Reg. No</th>
          <th>Remark</th>
          <th>Beneficiary</th>
          <th>% Share</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% land.forEach((l, index) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
            <td><%= l.nameOfLand %></td>
            <td><%= l.registrationNumber %></td>
            <td><%= l.typeRemark %></td>
            <td><%= l.beneficiaryName %></td>
            <td><%= l.share %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  <% } %>

  <h2>Executors</h2>
  <p>
    I appoint my elder brother <strong><%= executors.primaryName %></strong>, son of <strong><%= executors.primarySonOf %></strong>, resident of <strong><%= executors.primaryResidentOf %></strong>, to be the executor of this Will.
    If <%= executors.primaryName %> predeceases me, then my sister <strong><%= executors.alternateName %></strong>, daughter of <strong><%= executors.alternateDaughterOf %></strong>, residing at <strong><%= executors.alternateResidentOf %></strong>, will act as the executor of this Will.
  </p>

  <p>I hereby sign this will on <strong><%= testator.date %></strong> at <strong><%= testator.place %></strong>:</p>

  <div class="signature-block">
    <% [1, 2].forEach(i => { %>
      <div class="signature-item">
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p><strong>Witness <%= i %> (Sign)</strong></p>
        <p>Name:</p>
        <p>Address:</p>
        <p>Date:</p>
      </div>
    <% }) %>
    <div class="signature-item">
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
      <p><strong>Testator (Sign)</strong></p>
      <p>Name: <%= testator.name %></p>
      <p>Address: <%= testator.address %></p>
      <p>Date: <%= testator.date %></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="footer-note">Note: This document is a sample draft. Please consult a legal professional for review and notarization.</p>

</body>
</html>
